      "body": "PCLMULQDQ is not applicable to curves on a prime field, only ones on characteristic-2 fields (which I would avoid for cryptographic applications due to their worse security story, they also aren't widely used outside of some weird smartcard applications because of the history of aggressive patenting and enforcement).\r\n\r\nSo entirely not applicable here.\r\n\r\nWe do, however, use clmul in minisketch ( https://github.com/sipa/minisketch/ ), which uses a binary field.\r\n",
